---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="About Us" description="Learn about Personalized You — our mission to make meaningful handcrafted personalized experiences accessible and affordable.">
  <div style="max-width:700px;margin:0 auto;padding:4rem 2rem;">
    <h1 style="font-size:2.5rem;font-weight:800;margin-bottom:2rem;text-align:center;">About <span style="color:#8aab8e">Personalized You</span></h1>

    <div style="background:#eeebe6;border:1px solid #d9d3cc;border-radius:16px;padding:2.5rem;line-height:1.8;color:#2c2c2c;">
      <p style="margin-bottom:1.5rem;">
        We're a small business with a big belief: the most meaningful gifts aren't found on a shelf — they're created specifically for the person receiving them.
      </p>
      <p style="margin-bottom:1.5rem;">
        Personalized You was born from a simple observation: most digital products are generic. A meditation audio sounds the same for everyone. A children's story uses the same characters. We thought: <em style="color:#8aab8e">what if it didn't have to be that way?</em>
      </p>
      <p style="margin-bottom:1.5rem;">
        We craft experiences tailored to the individual with love and care — a bedtime story where <em>your</em> child is the hero, or a guided meditation that speaks to <em>your</em> exact goals and struggles.
      </p>
      <p style="margin-bottom:1.5rem;">
        Our mission: <strong style="color:#8aab8e">Making meaningful personalized experiences accessible and affordable.</strong>
      </p>
      <p>
        Every product is reviewed for quality before delivery. We believe technology should feel human — and when it's done right, it does.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(180px,1fr));gap:1.5rem;margin-top:2.5rem;text-align:center;">
      {[
        { icon: '❤️', label: 'Made with care' },
        { icon: '✍️', label: 'Crafted with love' },
        { icon: '⚡', label: 'Fast delivery' },
        { icon: '💰', label: 'Affordable prices' },
      ].map(v => (
        <div style="background:#eeebe6;border:1px solid #d9d3cc;border-radius:12px;padding:1.25rem;">
          <div style="font-size:2rem;margin-bottom:0.5rem;">{v.icon}</div>
          <p style="color:#7a7068;font-size:0.9rem;">{v.label}</p>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
